{"tid":1784761,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【黎小田設靈】陶傑撰輓聯悼念：「千歌淚傾湖海，問小我何能感絃歸夢宇。六劫愛繫心田，悵浮生幾許塵緣散胭脂。」","createTime":"2019-12-16T02:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T03:02:54.000Z","uid":35221,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08218ec78f3623eaae18864f812d6c533c13c06c","tid":1784761,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/80097067_3286267954779038_2464333680462528512_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=NlvFkgQLra8AQmuSI2soyJfiCey9KYu70hxgRhhUjw8eIIErnjKapT3Iw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=ff928cf2cb34783f185a0aa8f3139f2a&amp;oe=5E813FA3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F80097067_3286267954779038_2464333680462528512_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3DNlvFkgQLra8AQmuSI2soyJfiCey9KYu70hxgRhhUjw8eIIErnjKapT3Iw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dff928cf2cb34783f185a0aa8f3139f2a%26oe%3D5E813FA3&h=51b3c499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陶傑 Channel<br />\n已讚好的專頁 &middot; 9 小時 &middot; <br />\n <br />\n香港偉大的音樂家、好朋友黎小田今日設靈。<br />\n<br />\n他的一生豐麗多姿。我向小田敬撰輓聯：<br />\n<br />\n千歌淚傾<span style=\"color: red;\">湖海</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">問<ins>小</ins>我</span>何能感絃歸夢宇；<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">六劫</span>愛繫心<ins>田</ins>，悵<span style=\"color: red;\">浮生</span>幾許塵緣散<span style=\"color: red;\">胭脂</span>。<br />\n<br />\n內嵌他的幾首名曲的曲題，以及他的名字。我想他會喜歡。<br />\n<br />\n[按：<br />\n（陳秀雯〈湖海爭霸錄〉1980）<br />\n（陳麗斯〈問我〉1976）<br />\n（葉振棠〈浮生六劫〉1980）<br />\n（梅艷芳〈胭脂扣〉1987）]<br />\n<br />\n他的遺容安詳，像玩夠了又聽完了故事睡過去的一個五歲小孩。<br />\n<br />\n最後一次站在他面前道別，我涙下如雨。他的音樂，他的笑容，星辰昨夜，有良伴如此，真捨不得，一千一萬個捨不得⋯⋯"},{"pid":"39df1ccb2b6c9824ea69b055d4e4a5dd8992fa85","tid":1784761,"uid":100438,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77851b86c8a736c09b842cb53c7878500965e884","tid":1784761,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39df1ccb2b6c9824ea69b055d4e4a5dd8992fa85","tid":1784761,"uid":100438,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}